title: CardMaker - Summer 2016
description:
English | 100 pages | PDF | 34.5 MB

CardMaker magazine specializes in handcrafted greetings for all of life's occasions! Each issue of CardMaker brings you the latest in card-making ideas and paper projects, from birthday cards and thank you cards to new ideas for embellishing and easy ways to get the most out of your tools. You'll love the step-by-step technique articles featured in every issue
